Description: Upgrade your conference room with this Pro AV dock for seamless device connection without having to install any drivers. A plug-and-play solution that allows users to connect their device, focus entirely on their presentation, and avoid technical hassles. Optimized display settings for all projectors and monitors. With EDID technology, our Pro AV dock ensures that the resolution remains optimal and unchanged at 1080p. The function can be easily turned off using a mechanical on/off button. The Pro AV dock automatically turns off when the user disconnects their computer. This also includes other connected technology, such as speakers, cameras, and monitors. Recommended for use with one of our lockable cables for Pro AV. The lock prevents accidental disconnection and ensures an uninterrupted user experience. The Pro AV dock is PVC-free.
Notes: Smart Powercycle, ensures product is allways rebooted for the next user, engenous design enshures no overheating, EDID switch is awesome, and the locking USB-Cable ensures that the cable does not unplug accidentaly.
Extra notes: NO plastic, 100% recuclable cardbord box and included velcro straps!

Description: Connect your USB-C®-enabled laptop to your displays, accessories, and wired network with the versatile, elegant, and space-saving HP USB-C® Dock G5.Compatibility without constraints. Designed with universal compatibility in mind, this dock works with both HP and non-HP USB-C®- and Thunderbolt™-enabled laptops. Clear the clutter. Avoid a messy desk by using a simple one-cord setup that plugs in multiple devices."
Extra notes: basic dock, Certified for Poly X Series videobars.

Description: Vivolink 4K USB-C HUB – Your all-in-one solution for video conferencing systems. Connect all your equipment, just like you would with a docking station for your computer.The VLUSBCHUB2 is your key to effortless conferencing. Designed as a 4K USB-C Hub, it allows you to connect multiple devices via USB and share content seamlessly on a single screen. This Hub is designed to be fixed either under, or on top of, the desk to support all connections within a conference setting.

The HuddleHub Mini is a small but useful USB-C device that can act as a focal point in the smallest conference and meeting rooms. This box enables the sharing of a screen image with up to 4K 60hz resolution, at the same time that several USB devices such as speakers, camera,speakerphone etc. are connected together under the table, and hides all connections from the user. With a USB-C cable of up to 10 meters, you can reach the entire table with the connection cable, and easily and problem-free share images and content with internal and external meeting participants.
Extra notes: Seems to be a direct but bad copy of Unisynk Dock, 10m usb-c is a dream scenario, active cable reduces the possibilities die to Host and Tiers in USB chain and differt computers.
